<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/39486348" target="_blank" data-id="8001662" data-za-element-name="Title">
初级前端面试需要带什么作品？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/39486348/answer/81800457">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="28149300">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="81800457"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>122</a>
</div>

