<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/47047191" target="_blank" data-id="11032918" data-za-element-name="Title">
前端如何给 JavaScript 加密（不是混淆）？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/47047191/answer/121013968">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="43896660">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="121013968"> -->

