<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/36446304" target="_blank" data-id="6785578" data-za-element-name="Title">
React作为时下最热的前端框架，各位有什么经验分享下吗？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/36446304/answer/74688497">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="25298578">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="74688497"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>121</a>
</div>

