<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/38637676" target="_blank" data-id="7662419" data-za-element-name="Title">
参加第十届D2前端技术论坛，你有什么收获？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/38637676/answer/77516017">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="26432283">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="77516017"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>120</a>
</div>

