<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/36610007" target="_blank" data-id="6851176" data-za-element-name="Title">
极客学院推出的5k左右的前端就业班值得报名学习吗？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/36610007/answer/102831822">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="36588919">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="102831822"> -->

