<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/46952885" target="_blank" data-id="10995063" data-za-element-name="Title">
程序猿在工作时都是怎样打瞌睡的，有没有什么有趣的事情？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/46952885/answer/103591707">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="36893853">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="103591707"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>120</a>
</div>

