<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/46207738" target="_blank" data-id="10696744" data-za-element-name="Title">
花整个大学的时间研究前端好吗？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/46207738/answer/100503551">
